	* m/hp800.h (CANNOT_DUMP): Do not undef.

	* m/alpha.h: Fix comment.

	* s/usg5-4.h (HAVE_SYSVIPC): Remove, unused.
	(USG_SHARED_LIBRARIES): Remove, only used in unexec.c which is not
	used by this configuration.
