	Remove boilerplate comments.
	* s/hpux10-20.h (BAUD_CONVERT): Remove, same as the default.
	(HAVE_SYSVIPC): Remove, unused.
	(LD_SWITCH_SYSTEM_TEMACS): Simplify, hp9000s700 not supported anymore.

