	calculations for non-Truetype fonts.
	(x_draw_glyph_string): Sync with xterm.c.
	(x_draw_glyph_string_foreground) [USE_FONT_BACKEND]:
	Remove redundant code.
	(w32_initialize) [USE_FONT_BACKEND]: Call w32font_initialize.

