	* coding.c (Fdefine_coding_system_internal): Fix category setting
	for a coding system of type iso-2022.

2008-02-01  Kenichi Handa  <handa@m17n.org>

	* fontset.h (FS_LOAD_FONT): Call fs_load_font with the arg CHARSET -1.

