	* w32term.c (w32_term_init): Call add_keyboard_wait_descriptor.
	(w32_set_terminal_modes, w32_reset_terminal_modes): Add terminal arg.
	(x_clear_frame, x_delete_glyphs, w32_ring_bell, x_ins_del_lines):
	Add frame arg.
